Yet this magic will allow her to sneak into places and observe plots and schemes that could shake the foundations of Magistan, as the Empress’ progress approaches Norwood. OverviewTo advance the state of IPv6 support across the consumer electronics ecosystem, CEA and major U.S. carriers are organizing an IPv6 interoperability test event. Participants will have the opportunity to test their dual-stack (IPv4/IPv6) and IPv6 capable devices and applications with the carriers, carrier-supplied routers and IP formats that are widely deployed to millions of broadband consumers today.

UPnP Forum will be providing their IPv6 test tool for general use at the upcoming IPv6 interop event. John Berg from CableLabs will be there with a dedicated computer to run the test, but you may want to install the test tool on your own
